{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"19":"The Chapters on Manumission (of Slaves)"},"section_detail":{"19":{"hadithnumber_first":2512,"hadithnumber_last":2532,"arabicnumber_first":2512,"arabicnumber_last":2532}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2520,"arabicnumber":2520,"text":"Rapporté par Umm Salamah : Le Prophète (ﷺ) a dit : « Si l’une d’entre vous (les femmes) a un Mukatab, et qu’il a de quoi payer son contrat d’affranchissement, elle doit se voiler devant lui. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":19,"hadith":9}}]}